{"tid":329025,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講下各大機構補習社興趣班/功輔班嘅伏野","createTime":"2017-07-20T04:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T04:59:50.000Z","uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d27c73a9dea8c471fe765d08c1a2ba56c365ba58","tid":329025,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:46:41.000Z","msg":"返過幾間唔同機構 一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n[member]<br />\n1. 卓c教育<br />\n<br />\n暑期興趣班比嘅人工唔高 時薪只有70至100左右 <br />\n但勝在好易請人 無需太多經驗 又有好多班比你教<br />\n伏就伏在正式上堂之前要上佢嗰啲培訓<br />\n又要去攞啲物資<br />\n每堂都要寫lesson plan 上完堂之後又有份online問卷要你填<br />\n成個課程完咗之後仲要寫course evaluation 唔做齊唔出人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外佢有出常規既劍橋英語班 人工會高少少 時薪110-150<br />\n要全英語上堂 有教材比你 但都要做晒以上既文件紀錄<br />\n<br />\n2. 公x式<br />\n<br />\n呢間野周圍都係 好似7-11咁以franchise形式運作 人工睇老闆 兩年前我個19老闆出35蚊個鐘 而家睇jobs post好似40左右<br />\n<br />\n呢間野多數請教學助理 即係多數幫佢改簿 睇吓間野學生多唔多<br />\n多嘅話即係日日都係咁改簿 會好攰好悶好無聊 <br />\n<br />\n以數學功課為例 大部份一頁有20條數左右<br />\n最低level嘅數學練習就係20條 4+1 5+1 6+1 3+2 4+2 5+2等既題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除咗改簿之外 仲可能會叫你寫手冊 同家長講下學生情況<br />\n<br />\n[member]<br />\n<br />\n一陣分享啲冇咁伏既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3d90e8f9ed67ce0be21847a137d6a123fb9d4b","tid":329025,"uid":69091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060eea78197282b39bec43a97da797c95f8e6abe","tid":329025,"uid":125113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r